bug.short_desc: [Automation][Regression]Group does not work correctly in Chart

long_desc.thetext:
Description: Group does not work correctly in Chart.
Test Date: 20080102
Test Build: BIRT2.3.0 Daily Build: v20080102-1021
Step to reproduce:
1. Use the report attached 2. Preview it
Expect result: The 5th chart should be grouped as sum with interval 9.
Actual result: The sum result is incorrect.
I don't think the chart is wrong. If I display the same data in a table with a group of interval 9, it shows exactly the same values.

In old BIRT verision, base value of group of interval is the first value of series, but in lasted BIRT build, base value of group of interval is changed to zero. This kind of modification bring on group change. After disscuss with Heng Li, this behavior is expected, so close this bug and update related automation golden files.
